      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KALANI SEA (2) goes very well this trip starting 11 times for four wins and three minors. Comes off a (22.93) win last time, scoring by 5.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 400m at this track. Rates a leading player. BILLY BLINDERS (1) shapes well for this on her fast win a few runs back, getting around this track over 400m in 22.84 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Must include on winning run three back. TARAWI QUEENIE (8) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when third (22.58) at Gosford in a Grade 5. Well placed here and should do much better. RHAPSODY BEAST (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
